Plaques bearing its name are hanged outside a new sports complex and an impressive interactive museum dedicated to climate change.
“We are counting on him to bring about sustainable change,” said his friend and political ally Gabriel Olvera Hernandez, a member of Congress and the party of Peña Nieto, the PRI.
