Similarly, the final document mentions the political situation of Paraguay.
“We hope that this country’s electoral process will allow it to be reintegrated into the Union of South American Nations,” he said.
The need for Latin America to remain a region of prosperity and peace, integrated and having good relations with its neighbours, is another topic addressed at the summit.
